WEBVTT

00:00:56.600 --> 00:01:00.497
Bittu Sahgal: I have spent about 50 years

00:01:00.497 --> 00:01:03.551
mostly with children,

00:01:03.782 --> 00:01:04.996
for children.

00:01:05.219 --> 00:01:11.068
And I give them a simple 
lesson from my experience:

00:01:11.068 --> 00:01:15.151
that the world has only 
two political parties.

00:01:15.151 --> 00:01:20.113
One is the oldies, and other 
is the children’s party.

00:01:20.113 --> 00:01:25.430
And my daytime job 
is to protect

00:01:25.430 --> 00:01:28.430
the children’s party from the oldies!

00:01:28.430 --> 00:01:33.710
Their rivers, water, air 
should not get spoilt.